snippet.title: A Nightmare on Elm Street (1999) Fista Productions
snippet.description:
A Nightmare on Elm Street {release date: Nov 1999, size: 3.5 MB}

https://5kids2feed.itch.io/a-nightmare-on-elm-street-1999

This was the last game I finished back in the day before I disappeared for a while. Probably the most challenging out of the horror games I made. Control Freddy using the arrow keys & space bar.

Crappy graphics I made in mspaint and ripped sounds. I had a shit load of fun making it. Just the idea of making my own video game was amazing to me.
